<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>Currently you cannot configure Zend_Log to use a custom PHP 5.3 namespaced writer.</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code> 
$config = array(
    'mine' =&gt; array(
        'writerName'      =&gt; 'Writer',
        'writerNamespace' =&gt; '\Zfns\\',
    )
);

$logger = Zend_log::factory($config);
</code></pre>

<p>Will fail, as it will try to find a class with the name \Zfns_Writer in the path /Zfns/</p>

    </div>
</div>

